data.description: Welcome home to this newly remodeled home in bolivar. 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths. Possible 4th bedroom or second living space. Some updates include: Insulation in exterior walls and ceiling upstairs. All new electric on 2nd floor, both bathrooms, laundry room, kitchen. All new plumbing to both bathrooms and sink. Roof less than a year old. All new windows. New kitchen cabinets, counters. Both entry doors and interior doors. New flooring throughout. All new drywall and trim upstairs, kitchen, bath, laundry. You don’t want to miss this. Schedule your showing today!
